---
import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro";
import HelpNav from "../../components/HelpNav.astro";
---

<Layout title="Ayuda y Tutoriales">
    <HelpNav currentPath="/help" />
    <main class="space-y-8">

        <div>
            <h1 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-2">Ayuda y Tutoriales</h1>
            <p class="text-sm text-wa-text-secondary">Aprende a usar cada funcion de Agentic con guias paso a paso y ejemplos reales.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-5">

            <!-- Bots -->
            <a href="/help/bots" class="bg-wa-bg-panel border border-wa-border rounded-xl p-6 hover:border-wa-green/30 transition-colors group">
                <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-emerald-500/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
                    <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-emerald-400" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M8 10h.01M12 10h.01M16 10h.01M9 16H5a2 2 0 01-2-2V6a2 2 0 012-2h14a2 2 0 012 2v8a2 2 0 01-2 2h-5l-5 5v-5z" /></svg>
                </div>
                <h2 class="text-sm font-bold text-white mb-2 group-hover:text-wa-green transition-colors">Bots</h2>
                <p class="text-xs text-wa-text-secondary leading-relaxed">Crear, configurar y gestionar bots de WhatsApp. Conexion, pausar/reanudar, clonar y eliminar.</p>
                <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-1.5 mt-3">
                    <span class="px-2 py-0.5 bg-wa-bg-hover rounded text-[10px] text-wa-text-secondary">Crear bot</span>
                    <span class="px-2 py-0.5 bg-wa-bg-hover rounded text-[10px] text-wa-text-secondary">Conectar WhatsApp</span>
                    <span class="px-2 py-0.5 bg-wa-bg-hover rounded text-[10px] text-wa-text-secondary">Configurar IA</span>
                </div>
            </a>

            <!-- Flujos -->
            <a href="/help/flows" class="bg-wa-bg-panel border border-wa-border rounded-xl p-6 hover:border-wa-green/30 transition-colors group">
                <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-blue-500/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
                    <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-blue-400" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z" /></svg>
                </div>
                <h2 class="text-sm font-bold text-white mb-2 group-hover:text-wa-green transition-colors">Flujos de Automatizacion</h2>
                <p class="text-xs text-wa-text-secondary leading-relaxed">Crear flujos con triggers, pasos, condiciones y herramientas. El editor visual y como funciona cada tipo de paso.</p>
                <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-1.5 mt-3">
                    <span class="px-2 py-0.5 bg-wa-bg-hover rounded text-[10px] text-wa-text-secondary">Triggers</span>
                    <span class="px-2 py-0.5 bg-wa-bg-hover rounded text-[10px] text-wa-text-secondary">Pasos</span>
                    <span class="px-2 py-0.5 bg-wa-bg-hover rounded text-[10px] text-wa-text-secondary">Variables</span>
                </div>
            </a>

            <!-- Plantillas -->
            <a href="/help/templates" class="bg-wa-bg-panel border border-wa-border rounded-xl p-6 hover:border-wa-green/30 transition-colors group">
                <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-purple-500/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
                    <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-purple-400" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M4 5a1 1 0 011-1h14a1 1 0 011 1v2a1 1 0 01-1 1H5a1 1 0 01-1-1V5zM4 13a1 1 0 011-1h6a1 1 0 011 1v6a1 1 0 01-1 1H5a1 1 0 01-1-1v-6zM16 13a1 1 0 011-1h2a1 1 0 011 1v6a1 1 0 01-1 1h-2a1 1 0 01-1-1v-6z" /></svg>
                </div>
                <h2 class="text-sm font-bold text-white mb-2 group-hover:text-wa-green transition-colors">Plantillas</h2>
                <p class="text-xs text-wa-text-secondary leading-relaxed">Crear plantillas reutilizables para bots. Compartir configuraciones, flujos y variables entre multiples bots.</p>
                <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-1.5 mt-3">
                    <span class="px-2 py-0.5 bg-wa-bg-hover rounded text-[10px] text-wa-text-secondary">Crear plantilla</span>
                    <span class="px-2 py-0.5 bg-wa-bg-hover rounded text-[10px] text-wa-text-secondary">Reusar flujos</span>
                </div>
            </a>

            <!-- Campanas -->
            <a href="/help/campaigns" class="bg-wa-bg-panel border border-wa-border rounded-xl p-6 hover:border-wa-green/30 transition-colors group">
                <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-orange-500/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
                    <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-orange-400" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M11 5.882V19.24a1.76 1.76 0 01-3.417.592l-2.147-6.15M18 13a3 3 0 100-6M5.436 13.683A4.001 4.001 0 017 6h1.832c4.1 0 7.625-1.234 9.168-3v14c-1.543-1.766-5.067-3-9.168-3H7a3.988 3.988 0 01-1.564-.317z" /></svg>
                </div>
                <h2 class="text-sm font-bold text-white mb-2 group-hover:text-wa-green transition-colors">Campanas de Facebook</h2>
                <p class="text-xs text-wa-text-secondary leading-relaxed">Crear y gestionar campanas publicitarias. Segmentacion, presupuestos, anuncios y boost de publicaciones.</p>
                <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-1.5 mt-3">
                    <span class="px-2 py-0.5 bg-wa-bg-hover rounded text-[10px] text-wa-text-secondary">Crear campana</span>
                    <span class="px-2 py-0.5 bg-wa-bg-hover rounded text-[10px] text-wa-text-secondary">Segmentacion</span>
                    <span class="px-2 py-0.5 bg-wa-bg-hover rounded text-[10px] text-wa-text-secondary">Boost posts</span>
                </div>
            </a>

            <!-- Finanzas -->
            <a href="/help/finance" class="bg-wa-bg-panel border border-wa-border rounded-xl p-6 hover:border-wa-green/30 transition-colors group">
                <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-wa-green/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
                    <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-wa-green" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8c-1.657 0-3 .895-3 2s1.343 2 3 2 3 .895 3 2-1.343 2-3 2m0-8c1.11 0 2.08.402 2.599 1M12 8V7m0 1v8m0 0v1m0-1c-1.11 0-2.08-.402-2.599-1M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" /></svg>
                </div>
                <h2 class="text-sm font-bold text-white mb-2 group-hover:text-wa-green transition-colors">Control Financiero</h2>
                <p class="text-xs text-wa-text-secondary leading-relaxed">Registrar ingresos, gastos, gestionar periodos y ver reportes P&L. Asignar trabajadores y cuentas bancarias.</p>
                <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-1.5 mt-3">
                    <span class="px-2 py-0.5 bg-wa-bg-hover rounded text-[10px] text-wa-text-secondary">Ingresos/Gastos</span>
                    <span class="px-2 py-0.5 bg-wa-bg-hover rounded text-[10px] text-wa-text-secondary">P&L</span>
                    <span class="px-2 py-0.5 bg-wa-bg-hover rounded text-[10px] text-wa-text-secondary">Periodos</span>
                </div>
            </a>

            <!-- Monitoreo -->
            <a href="/help/monitor" class="bg-wa-bg-panel border border-wa-border rounded-xl p-6 hover:border-wa-green/30 transition-colors group">
                <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-yellow-500/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
                    <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-yellow-400" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 19v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2zm0 0V9a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v10m-6 0a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2m0 0V5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v14a2 2 0 01-2 2h-2a2 2 0 01-2-2z" /></svg>
                </div>
                <h2 class="text-sm font-bold text-white mb-2 group-hover:text-wa-green transition-colors">Monitoreo y Logs</h2>
                <p class="text-xs text-wa-text-secondary leading-relaxed">Monitorear conversaciones en tiempo real, ver logs del sistema, emular bots y depurar flujos.</p>
                <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-1.5 mt-3">
                    <span class="px-2 py-0.5 bg-wa-bg-hover rounded text-[10px] text-wa-text-secondary">Sesiones</span>
                    <span class="px-2 py-0.5 bg-wa-bg-hover rounded text-[10px] text-wa-text-secondary">Emulador</span>
                    <span class="px-2 py-0.5 bg-wa-bg-hover rounded text-[10px] text-wa-text-secondary">Logs</span>
                </div>
            </a>

        </div>

        <!-- Quick Tips -->
        <div class="bg-wa-bg-panel border border-wa-border rounded-xl p-6">
            <h2 class="text-sm font-bold text-white mb-4">Primeros pasos</h2>
            <div class="space-y-3">
                <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
                    <span class="w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-wa-green/20 text-wa-green text-xs font-bold flex items-center justify-center shrink-0 mt-0.5">1</span>
                    <div>
                        <p class="text-sm text-white font-medium">Crea tu primer bot</p>
                        <p class="text-xs text-wa-text-secondary mt-0.5">Ve a <a href="/bots" class="text-wa-green hover:underline">Bots</a> y haz clic en "+ Crear Bot". Dale un nombre y plataforma.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
                    <span class="w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-wa-green/20 text-wa-green text-xs font-bold flex items-center justify-center shrink-0 mt-0.5">2</span>
                    <div>
                        <p class="text-sm text-white font-medium">Conecta WhatsApp</p>
                        <p class="text-xs text-wa-text-secondary mt-0.5">Dentro del bot, genera un enlace publico y escanea el codigo QR con tu telefono.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
                    <span class="w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-wa-green/20 text-wa-green text-xs font-bold flex items-center justify-center shrink-0 mt-0.5">3</span>
                    <div>
                        <p class="text-sm text-white font-medium">Crea un flujo de respuesta</p>
                        <p class="text-xs text-wa-text-secondary mt-0.5">Agrega un flujo con un trigger (ej: "hola") y pasos de respuesta. Pruebalo con el emulador.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
                    <span class="w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-wa-green/20 text-wa-green text-xs font-bold flex items-center justify-center shrink-0 mt-0.5">4</span>
                    <div>
                        <p class="text-sm text-white font-medium">Conecta Facebook (opcional)</p>
                        <p class="text-xs text-wa-text-secondary mt-0.5">Ve a <a href="/finance/settings" class="text-wa-green hover:underline">Finanzas &gt; Config</a> para conectar Facebook y gestionar campanas.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

    </main>
</Layout>
